    dc:description "Figure 22. Poa wendtii Soreng & P. M. Peterson A habit B culm C inflorescence D blade apex E ligule F spikelet G lower glume H upper glume I floret. Drawn from the holotype collection (Wendt 883 & Riskind)." ;
