    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10158>
    dc:description "Figure 23. Poa wendtii Soreng & P. M. Peterson A lemma B lemma abaxial view C palea dorsal view D palea ventral view E perfect flower enclosed in palea with lodicules, pistil, and stamen filaments F perfect flower with pistil / partly developed caryopsis G lodicules and rachilla internode H caryopsis ventral view, with sulcus and hilum I caryopsis dorsal view. Drawn from the holotype collection (Wendt 883 & Riskind)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10158" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

